                         The NCATB superelastic alloy also undergoes a large change in spontaneous magnetization induced by the martensitic transformation. No apparent change in magnetization due to thermal martensitic transformation was detected in the thermomagnetization curves (fig. S4), because the transformation hardly proceeds during cooling (
