                             Fig. 3
                         ); hence, we obtain hexamer under these conditions. The greater susceptibility of the hexamer to fragmentation upon shaking can be rationalized, as the macrocycles in the hexamer fibers are able to form fewer &#x03B2; sheets than those in the heptamer fibers.
                     

