                          and table S3; see table S4 for deactivation kinetics in nucleated patches). The difference in &#x03C4;
                             deact
                          was much more pronounced in the presence of CTZ (fig. S4A and table S3).
                     

                         There was no difference in the desensitization time constant (&#x03C4;
