                          (fig. S5B and table S4). The effect of CKAMP44 on desensitization was also reflected in a more pronounced desensitization 10 ms after a short glutamate pulse, and a significantly slower recovery from desensitization in nucleated patches from CKAMP44-overexpressing CA1 cells but, in contrast, in a reduced desensitization and faster recovery from desensitization in nucleated patches from CKAMP44 KO CA1 cells (
